<li><code v-pre>k = +inf</code> with cooldown: <a href="#q309-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-with-cooldown">Q309</a>. We don't need state <code v-pre>k</code> anymore. <code v-pre>j</code> have 4 possible states instead of 2.</li>
